{"tid":321183,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[細數] 保方職業生涯裡面，總共阻住過幾多個龍上位？","createTime":"2017-07-14T05:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T07:34:26.000Z","uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5736b47ffefb09a02c65d212e8f3f675b86a411a","tid":321183,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"雖然保方真係好癲，但對其他意大利龍門嚟講可以話係一大屏障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nToldo，De sanctis，Abbiati，Sirigu，Perin呢啲喺球會守得幾好都冇用，國家隊都冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當拿隆馬好彩在遲出世，撞正保方終於肯退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家印象中仲有邊啲經典例子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a6af577e736fe7753b8d31142ca5aa2b4a4f40","tid":321183,"uid":40668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"托度算好，係euro 都表演過 ,其他真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467ed8390b812d3aab3edc9172dd7f999ac3e8ab","tid":321183,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>托度算好，係euro 都表演過 ,其他真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啱保方傷咗先有機會踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6039370f2549bb1eca140d269afc49b836e1a3dc","tid":321183,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"當拿隆馬"},{"pid":"33956dc83202b2ee1eb8b4aa943287d73605a0c4","tid":321183,"uid":56203,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T05:51:34.000Z","msg":"雲達沙都曾經俾保方壓住"},{"pid":"d54cff4d7df8fa30d858b73fe87a42a35272b9b4","tid":321183,"uid":54524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c